TaskRequirements
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 - Useable <TaskRequirements> - 
*NOTE* other than going by the name i don't have much more information on them.


	CanMoveWhenGuarding
	EquipLongGunWhenIdle
	EquipSidearmWhenIdle
	Guard
	None
	Patrol
	StandardScenario
	
	Some single line examples:	

	1.	<TaskRequirements>None</TaskRequirements>	
	
	2.	<TaskRequirements>Guard</TaskRequirements>
	
	3.	<TaskRequirements>Patrol</TaskRequirements>
		  		  
	4.	<TaskRequirements>Guard CanMoveWhenGuarding Patrol</TaskRequirements>	
		  		
	5.	<TaskRequirements>Guard CanMoveWhenGuarding EquipSidearmWhenIdle</TaskRequirements>

	 
