 ForcedScenarios 
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

 - Some Useable <ForcedScenarios> -


	1.	<string>WORLD_HUMAN_HANG_OUT_STREET</string>
	
	2.	<string>WORLD_HUMAN_DRINKING</string>
	
	3.	<string>WORLD_HUMAN_SMOKING</string>
	
	4.	<string>WORLD_HUMAN_SMOKING_POT</string>
	
	5.	<string>WORLD_HUMAN_DRUG_DEALER</string>
	
	6.	<string>WORLD_HUMAN_STAND_MOBILE</string>
.

When a Ped is spawned into the LSR world it will use 1 of the ForcedScenarios that's been listed.
	 
 an example snippet:
		  
		<ForcedScenarios>
			<string>WORLD_HUMAN_HANG_OUT_STREET</string>
			<string>WORLD_HUMAN_DRINKING</string>
			<string>WORLD_HUMAN_SMOKING</string>
			<string>WORLD_HUMAN_SMOKING_POT</string>
			<string>WORLD_HUMAN_DRUG_DEALER</string>
			<string>WORLD_HUMAN_STAND_MOBILE</string>
		</ForcedScenarios>	

*Note* other Scenarios can found be @ https://wiki.rage.mp/index.php?title=Scenarios 
or by searching online and using one of the ForcedScenarios names "WORLD_HUMAN_SMOKING_POT" for a more detailed search result.	 
